<h2 id="so-simple-theme-is-all-about">So Simple Theme is all about:</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Responsive templates. Looking good on mobile, tablet, and desktop.</li>
  <li>Gracefully degrading in older browsers. Compatible with Internet Explorer 9+ and all modern browsers.</li>
  <li>Minimal embellishments and subtle animations.</li>
  <li>Optional large feature images for posts and pages.</li>
  <li><a href="http://localhost:4000/404.html">Custom 404 page</a> to get you started.</li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/christian-fei/Simple-Jekyll-Search">Simple site search</a></li>
  <li>Support for Disqus Comments</li>
</ul>

